name: Navy Merino Wool Knit Half Zip
description: Crafted in the breathtaking Himalayas of Nepal, infusing each garment with a sense of place and tradition. Made from high-quality, locally sourced Merino Wool that offer comfort, durability, and a luxurious feel.
short_description: Made from 100% Australian Merino Wool. Sourced locally from the foothills of Nepalese Himalayas. Knitted by the locals.

variations.uagb_excerpt: VUE LUXE, A premium apparel clothing series. The Cotton Set gives you the perfect look whilst maintaining the comfort. Ultra Richness is reflected through the fabric that is carefully hand-picked after hours of searching and then carefully hand stitched to perfection.

variations.name: Deana Harlandé Himalayan Wool Sweater
variations.description:
Exquisite Himalayan Wool Sweater


Experience the unparalleled luxury of our premium sweater, crafted from the highest quality wool sourced from the majestic Himalayan sheep of Nepal. Each strand of wool embodies the pristine essence of the Himalayas, ensuring a garment that is not only soft and lightweight but also remarkably warm and durable, making it your perfect companion for those cold, dark days.


Our sweater is a testament to the exceptional craftsmanship of skilled Nepali artisans, who pour their expertise and passion into every stitch. These experienced workers have honed their skills over generations, blending traditional techniques with contemporary designs to create a masterpiece that is both unique and timeless.


Wrap yourself in the warmth and elegance of our Himalayan wool sweater, and let it become a cherished addition to your wardrobe. Whether you're braving the winter chill or simply seeking a touch of luxury, this sweater promises to deliver comfort, style, and a connection to the rich heritage of the Himalayas.
variations.short_description:
Himalayan Wool Sweater


Discover the luxury of our premium sweater, crafted from the finest wool of Himalayan sheep from Nepal. Soft, lightweight, and warm, it’s perfect for cold, dark days. This unique sweater showcases the exceptional craftsmanship of skilled Nepali artisans, blending traditional techniques with contemporary design. Each piece supports the hardworking artisans and captures the essence of the Himalayas, offering you unmatched comfort and style. Wrap yourself in this exquisite garment and experience the rich heritage and quality of the Himalayas.

meta_data.value: Discover the luxury of our premium woolen sweater, crafted from the finest wool of Himalayan sheep. Limited Pieces available.

variations.uagb_excerpt: Himalayan Wool Sweater Discover the luxury of our premium sweater, crafted from the finest wool of Himalayan sheep from Nepal. Soft, lightweight, and warm, it's perfect for cold, dark days. This unique sweater showcases the exceptional craftsmanship of skilled Nepali artisans, blending traditional techniques with contemporary design. Each piece supports the hardworking artisans and captures…

variations.name: Sovrana in Black by Deana Harlandé
variations.description: Made from high-quality, locally sourced ZH Chiffon yarn that offers comfort, durability, and a luxurious feel.
variations.short_description: Sovrana, a piece that embodies luxury, tradition, and meticulous artistry. Each garment is handmade with extreme delicacy and care, ensuring that every stitch reflects our commitment to quality and excellence.

variations.uagb_excerpt: VUE LUXE, A premium apparel clothing series. The Cotton Set gives you the perfect look whilst maintaining the comfort. Ultra Richness is reflected through the fabric that is carefully hand-picked after hours of searching and then carefully hand stitched to perfection.

variations.name: Deana Harlandé Himalayan Wool Sweater
variations.description:
Exquisite Himalayan Wool Sweater


Experience the unparalleled luxury of our premium sweater, crafted from the highest quality wool sourced from the majestic Himalayan sheep of Nepal. Each strand of wool embodies the pristine essence of the Himalayas, ensuring a garment that is not only soft and lightweight but also remarkably warm and durable, making it your perfect companion for those cold, dark days.


Our sweater is a testament to the exceptional craftsmanship of skilled Nepali artisans, who pour their expertise and passion into every stitch. These experienced workers have honed their skills over generations, blending traditional techniques with contemporary designs to create a masterpiece that is both unique and timeless.


Wrap yourself in the warmth and elegance of our Himalayan wool sweater, and let it become a cherished addition to your wardrobe. Whether you're braving the winter chill or simply seeking a touch of luxury, this sweater promises to deliver comfort, style, and a connection to the rich heritage of the Himalayas.
variations.short_description:
Himalayan Wool Sweater


Discover the luxury of our premium sweater, crafted from the finest wool of Himalayan sheep from Nepal. Soft, lightweight, and warm, it’s perfect for cold, dark days. This unique sweater showcases the exceptional craftsmanship of skilled Nepali artisans, blending traditional techniques with contemporary design. Each piece supports the hardworking artisans and captures the essence of the Himalayas, offering you unmatched comfort and style. Wrap yourself in this exquisite garment and experience the rich heritage and quality of the Himalayas.

meta_data.value: Discover the luxury of our premium woolen sweater, crafted from the finest wool of Himalayan sheep. Limited Pieces available.

name: Sovrana in White by Deana Harlandé
description: Made from high-quality, locally sourced materials that offer comfort, durability, and a luxurious feel.
short_description: Sovrana, a piece that embodies luxury, tradition, and meticulous artistry. Each garment is handmade with extreme delicacy and care, ensuring that every stitch reflects our commitment to quality and excellence.

variations.description: Crafted in the breathtaking Himalayas of Nepal, infusing each garment with a sense of place and tradition. Made from high-quality, locally sourced Merino Wool that offer comfort, durability, and a luxurious feel.
variations.short_description: Made from 100% Australian Merino Wool. Sourced locally from the foothills of Nepalese Himalayas. Knitted by the locals.

variations.uagb_excerpt: Made from 100% Australian Merino Wool. Sourced locally from the foothills of Nepalese Himalayas. Knitted by the locals.

variations.name: Grey Textured Polo Sweater
variations.short_description: VUE LUXE, A premium apparel clothing series. The sweater gives you the perfect look whilst maintaining the comfort. Ultra Richness is reflected through the fabric that is carefully hand-picked after hours of searching and then carefully hand stitched to perfection.

meta_data.value: The fabric that in Deana Harlande VUE LUXE Cotton Set is carefully hand-picked after hours of searching and then carefully hand stitched to perfection.

variations.uagb_excerpt: VUE LUXE, A premium apparel clothing series. The Cotton Set gives you the perfect look whilst maintaining the comfort. Ultra Richness is reflected through the fabric that is carefully hand-picked after hours of searching and then carefully hand stitched to perfection.

variations.name: Deana Harlandé Himalayan Wool Sweater
variations.description:
Exquisite Himalayan Wool Sweater


Experience the unparalleled luxury of our premium sweater, crafted from the highest quality wool sourced from the majestic Himalayan sheep of Nepal. Each strand of wool embodies the pristine essence of the Himalayas, ensuring a garment that is not only soft and lightweight but also remarkably warm and durable, making it your perfect companion for those cold, dark days.


Our sweater is a testament to the exceptional craftsmanship of skilled Nepali artisans, who pour their expertise and passion into every stitch. These experienced workers have honed their skills over generations, blending traditional techniques with contemporary designs to create a masterpiece that is both unique and timeless.


Wrap yourself in the warmth and elegance of our Himalayan wool sweater, and let it become a cherished addition to your wardrobe. Whether you're braving the winter chill or simply seeking a touch of luxury, this sweater promises to deliver comfort, style, and a connection to the rich heritage of the Himalayas.
variations.short_description:
Himalayan Wool Sweater


Discover the luxury of our premium sweater, crafted from the finest wool of Himalayan sheep from Nepal. Soft, lightweight, and warm, it’s perfect for cold, dark days. This unique sweater showcases the exceptional craftsmanship of skilled Nepali artisans, blending traditional techniques with contemporary design. Each piece supports the hardworking artisans and captures the essence of the Himalayas, offering you unmatched comfort and style. Wrap yourself in this exquisite garment and experience the rich heritage and quality of the Himalayas.

uagb_excerpt: Sovrana, a piece that embodies luxury, tradition, and meticulous artistry. Each garment is handmade with extreme delicacy and care, ensuring that every stitch reflects our commitment to quality and excellence.

name: Deana Harlandé VUE LUXE Cotton Set
description: VUE LUXE, a premium apparel series, combines style with comfort in every piece. The Cotton Set gives you a refined look with the cozy feel of high-quality fabric. Each piece is crafted from carefully chosen materials and expertly hand-stitched to reflect true luxury.
short_description: VUE LUXE, A premium apparel clothing series. The Cotton Set gives you the perfect look whilst maintaining the comfort. Ultra Richness is reflected through the fabric that is carefully hand-picked after hours of searching and then carefully hand stitched to perfection.

variations.name: Navy Merino Wool Knit Half Zip
variations.description: Crafted in the breathtaking Himalayas of Nepal, infusing each garment with a sense of place and tradition. Made from high-quality, locally sourced Merino Wool that offer comfort, durability, and a luxurious feel.
variations.short_description: Made from 100% Australian Merino Wool. Sourced locally from the foothills of Nepalese Himalayas. Knitted by the locals.

variations.uagb_excerpt: VUE LUXE, A premium apparel clothing series. The Cotton Set gives you the perfect look whilst maintaining the comfort. Ultra Richness is reflected through the fabric that is carefully hand-picked after hours of searching and then carefully hand stitched to perfection.

variations.name: Deana Harlandé Himalayan Wool Sweater
variations.description:
Exquisite Himalayan Wool Sweater


Experience the unparalleled luxury of our premium sweater, crafted from the highest quality wool sourced from the majestic Himalayan sheep of Nepal. Each strand of wool embodies the pristine essence of the Himalayas, ensuring a garment that is not only soft and lightweight but also remarkably warm and durable, making it your perfect companion for those cold, dark days.


Our sweater is a testament to the exceptional craftsmanship of skilled Nepali artisans, who pour their expertise and passion into every stitch. These experienced workers have honed their skills over generations, blending traditional techniques with contemporary designs to create a masterpiece that is both unique and timeless.


Wrap yourself in the warmth and elegance of our Himalayan wool sweater, and let it become a cherished addition to your wardrobe. Whether you're braving the winter chill or simply seeking a touch of luxury, this sweater promises to deliver comfort, style, and a connection to the rich heritage of the Himalayas.
variations.short_description:
Himalayan Wool Sweater


Discover the luxury of our premium sweater, crafted from the finest wool of Himalayan sheep from Nepal. Soft, lightweight, and warm, it’s perfect for cold, dark days. This unique sweater showcases the exceptional craftsmanship of skilled Nepali artisans, blending traditional techniques with contemporary design. Each piece supports the hardworking artisans and captures the essence of the Himalayas, offering you unmatched comfort and style. Wrap yourself in this exquisite garment and experience the rich heritage and quality of the Himalayas.

meta_data.value: Discover the luxury of our premium woolen sweater, crafted from the finest wool of Himalayan sheep. Limited Pieces available.

uagb_excerpt: VUE LUXE, A premium apparel clothing series. The Cotton Set gives you the perfect look whilst maintaining the comfort. Ultra Richness is reflected through the fabric that is carefully hand-picked after hours of searching and then carefully hand stitched to perfection.

name: Deana Harlandé Himalayan Wool Sweater
description:
Exquisite Himalayan Wool Sweater


Experience the unparalleled luxury of our premium sweater, crafted from the highest quality wool sourced from the majestic Himalayan sheep of Nepal. Each strand of wool embodies the pristine essence of the Himalayas, ensuring a garment that is not only soft and lightweight but also remarkably warm and durable, making it your perfect companion for those cold, dark days.


Our sweater is a testament to the exceptional craftsmanship of skilled Nepali artisans, who pour their expertise and passion into every stitch. These experienced workers have honed their skills over generations, blending traditional techniques with contemporary designs to create a masterpiece that is both unique and timeless.


Wrap yourself in the warmth and elegance of our Himalayan wool sweater, and let it become a cherished addition to your wardrobe. Whether you're braving the winter chill or simply seeking a touch of luxury, this sweater promises to deliver comfort, style, and a connection to the rich heritage of the Himalayas.
short_description:
Himalayan Wool Sweater


Discover the luxury of our premium sweater, crafted from the finest wool of Himalayan sheep from Nepal. Soft, lightweight, and warm, it’s perfect for cold, dark days. This unique sweater showcases the exceptional craftsmanship of skilled Nepali artisans, blending traditional techniques with contemporary design. Each piece supports the hardworking artisans and captures the essence of the Himalayas, offering you unmatched comfort and style. Wrap yourself in this exquisite garment and experience the rich heritage and quality of the Himalayas.

variations.name: Navy Merino Wool Knit Half Zip
variations.description: Crafted in the breathtaking Himalayas of Nepal, infusing each garment with a sense of place and tradition. Made from high-quality, locally sourced Merino Wool that offer comfort, durability, and a luxurious feel.
variations.short_description: Made from 100% Australian Merino Wool. Sourced locally from the foothills of Nepalese Himalayas. Knitted by the locals.

variations.uagb_excerpt: VUE LUXE, A premium apparel clothing series. The Cotton Set gives you the perfect look whilst maintaining the comfort. Ultra Richness is reflected through the fabric that is carefully hand-picked after hours of searching and then carefully hand stitched to perfection.

variations.name: Deana Harlandé Himalayan Wool Sweater
variations.description:
Exquisite Himalayan Wool Sweater


Experience the unparalleled luxury of our premium sweater, crafted from the highest quality wool sourced from the majestic Himalayan sheep of Nepal. Each strand of wool embodies the pristine essence of the Himalayas, ensuring a garment that is not only soft and lightweight but also remarkably warm and durable, making it your perfect companion for those cold, dark days.


Our sweater is a testament to the exceptional craftsmanship of skilled Nepali artisans, who pour their expertise and passion into every stitch. These experienced workers have honed their skills over generations, blending traditional techniques with contemporary designs to create a masterpiece that is both unique and timeless.


Wrap yourself in the warmth and elegance of our Himalayan wool sweater, and let it become a cherished addition to your wardrobe. Whether you're braving the winter chill or simply seeking a touch of luxury, this sweater promises to deliver comfort, style, and a connection to the rich heritage of the Himalayas.
variations.short_description:
Himalayan Wool Sweater


Discover the luxury of our premium sweater, crafted from the finest wool of Himalayan sheep from Nepal. Soft, lightweight, and warm, it’s perfect for cold, dark days. This unique sweater showcases the exceptional craftsmanship of skilled Nepali artisans, blending traditional techniques with contemporary design. Each piece supports the hardworking artisans and captures the essence of the Himalayas, offering you unmatched comfort and style. Wrap yourself in this exquisite garment and experience the rich heritage and quality of the Himalayas.

meta_data.value: Discover the luxury of our premium woolen sweater, crafted from the finest wool of Himalayan sheep. Limited Pieces available.

variations.uagb_excerpt: VUE LUXE, A premium apparel clothing series. The Cotton Set gives you the perfect look whilst maintaining the comfort. Ultra Richness is reflected through the fabric that is carefully hand-picked after hours of searching and then carefully hand stitched to perfection.

variations.name: Deana Harlandé Himalayan Wool Sweater
variations.description:
Exquisite Himalayan Wool Sweater


Experience the unparalleled luxury of our premium sweater, crafted from the highest quality wool sourced from the majestic Himalayan sheep of Nepal. Each strand of wool embodies the pristine essence of the Himalayas, ensuring a garment that is not only soft and lightweight but also remarkably warm and durable, making it your perfect companion for those cold, dark days.


Our sweater is a testament to the exceptional craftsmanship of skilled Nepali artisans, who pour their expertise and passion into every stitch. These experienced workers have honed their skills over generations, blending traditional techniques with contemporary designs to create a masterpiece that is both unique and timeless.


Wrap yourself in the warmth and elegance of our Himalayan wool sweater, and let it become a cherished addition to your wardrobe. Whether you're braving the winter chill or simply seeking a touch of luxury, this sweater promises to deliver comfort, style, and a connection to the rich heritage of the Himalayas.
variations.short_description:
Himalayan Wool Sweater


Discover the luxury of our premium sweater, crafted from the finest wool of Himalayan sheep from Nepal. Soft, lightweight, and warm, it’s perfect for cold, dark days. This unique sweater showcases the exceptional craftsmanship of skilled Nepali artisans, blending traditional techniques with contemporary design. Each piece supports the hardworking artisans and captures the essence of the Himalayas, offering you unmatched comfort and style. Wrap yourself in this exquisite garment and experience the rich heritage and quality of the Himalayas.

meta_data.value: Discover the luxury of our premium woolen sweater, crafted from the finest wool of Himalayan sheep. Limited Pieces available.
